des:
Real Life Radio AZ: Where Arizona's heartbeat is amplified through the airwaves! Born from local roots, we're a one-of-a-kind station playing everything from EDM to Metal, with a special love for local artists. No hoops, just real support and a wild, 'hand-the-aux-cord-to-that-one-friend' vibe every night. Tune in, discover new favorites, and join our journey of music, art, and community.

Broadcasting world-wide from Phoenix Arizona, Real Life Radio AZ strives to give some exposure to local art and artists from throughout the state of Arizona. No tricks. No hoops. Just real support.
